---
title: Pork Feijoada with Basmati Rice
description: Feijoada is a meaty version of the Brazilian staple dish of cooked black beans, feijão, using pork mince to create a beautifully rich flavour. Traditionally prepared over a low heat in a clay pot and simmered for an hour, tonight’s recipe will prove that you can create the same flavour in double aquick time. 20 minute recipes don’t get more delicious than this one!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-feijoada-56f4be85-43b950d0.jpg
